# 🚀 My Projects Portfolio

Welcome to my GitHub portfolio!  
This repository highlights the projects I’ve worked on across virtualization, monitoring, system administration, and web development. Each project demonstrates practical implementations of industry tools and technologies.  

---

## 📂 Projects Overview

### 🔹 [Proxmox + Zabbix](./Proxmox-Zabbix)
- **Description:** Built a Proxmox Virtual Environment to host multiple VMs and integrated Zabbix for monitoring.  
- **Technologies:** Proxmox VE, Zabbix, Linux, Networking  
- **Highlights:**
  - Set up virtualization cluster on Proxmox
  - Monitored VM performance and availability with Zabbix
  - Configured email alerts for critical system failures  

---

### 🔹 [WordPress Deployment](./WordPress-Project)
- **Description:** Designed and deployed a WordPress website with scalability in mind.  
- **Technologies:** WordPress, MySQL, Apache/Nginx, Cloudflare  
- **Highlights:**
  - Installed and configured WordPress on Linux server  
  - Secured site with HTTPS (SSL/TLS)  
  - Managed domain through Cloudflare  

---

### 🔹 [Windows Server 2019 Lab](./Windows-Server-2019)
- **Description:** Configured a Windows Server 2019 environment with Active Directory, Group Policies, and Domain Services.  
- **Technologies:** Windows Server 2019, Active Directory, DNS, DHCP  
- **Highlights:**
  - Setup of AD DS forest/domain structure  
  - Group Policy Objects (GPOs) for security hardening  
  - DHCP & DNS configuration for network automation  

---

### 🔹 [Linux Client Configurations](./Linux-Client)
- **Description:** Managed Linux clients integrated into Windows and Proxmox environments.  
- **Technologies:** Ubuntu, CentOS/Rocky, Shell Scripting  
- **Highlights:**
  - Configured clients for domain authentication  
  - Automated tasks using Bash scripts  
  - Implemented secure SSH access and firewall rules  

---

## 🛠️ Skills & Tools Demonstrated
- Virtualization: **Proxmox VE, Hyper-V**  
- Monitoring: **Zabbix**  
- Web Hosting: **WordPress, Apache, Nginx, Cloudflare**  
- Systems: **Windows Server 2019, Linux (Ubuntu, Rocky, Debian)**  
- Networking: **VLANs, DNS, DHCP, AD DS**  
- Scripting & Automation: **Bash, PowerShell**  

